0) Lets say jvsim sandbox root is $SB, for example /homes/juniper/jvsim/

1) Build the sources
   cd $SB;
   make;

2) Check if all the following executables are in $ROOT/bin/[mac/linux]
   agent_server, agent_client, agent_test, mosquitto

3) Set the environment variable, ROOTPATH. For bash, do that following
   export ROOTPATH=$SB

4) Run the simulator and the test client
   cd $ROOT/bin
   ./jvsim -s -t

5) The Logs will be generated in $ROOT/logs/

